title: 11/09: Mailbag! (Record Fri.) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
The latest injury updates, some DFS advice and a bunch of your questions via Apple Podcasts and email. We'll try to figure out who to start Latavius Murray over. We'll help you with some trades and of course we'll do some Regulating.
